      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive engineering, this high-revving icon features a meticulously maintained naturally aspirated inline-six power plant. The engine exhibits optimal compression across all cylinders, benefiting from a recent valve adjustment and a comprehensive cooling system overhaul. Power is delivered through a crisp, short-throw six-speed manual transmission to a rear-mounted limited-slip differential, ensuring linear torque delivery and exceptional corner-exit traction. The chassis remains taut, featuring upgraded polyurethane bushings and reinforced subframe mounts to eliminate common structural fatigue. Riding on lightweight forged alloys wrapped in high-performance compound rubber, the suspension geometry is dialed for neutral handling with adjustable coilover damping. This vehicle represents a turn-key opportunity for the discerning collector seeking peak mechanical integrity and visceral driver engagement.",
