      "description": "This 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman S is a true showroom-quality specimen, meticulously maintained to satisfy the most demanding enthusiast. Finished in a flawless Guards Red with a deep, glass-like ceramic coating, the exterior is entirely free of rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Inside, the black leather interior retains its factory-fresh scent and firm bolsters, with zero wear on the touchpoints or carpets. Mechanically, it is indistinguishable from new, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a full paper trail included. Always garage-kept under a soft cover and never driven in inclement weather, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of the 'mint' standard. It features the Sport Chrono package, premium Bose surround sound, and 20-inch Carrera S wheels wrapped in fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. This is a rare opportunity to own a modern classic that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line.",
